# devtools::install_github("ryantimpe/brickr")
library(tidyverse)
library(brickr)
library(jpeg)
library(png)
mosaic <- readJPEG("Early_placental_structure.jpg") %>% 
  scale_image(c(160,80)) %>% 
  legoize() %>% 
  collect_bricks()
mosaic %>% 
  display_set()
